Nigerian actress and fashion blogger, Temi Otedola, has announced her engagement to her long time lover and boyfriend, Nigerian singer, Oluwatosin Ajibade, popularly known as Mr Eazi. She revealed this on Sunday via her Instagram page, with a video of the singer proposing to her. Nigerian disc jockey, Florence Otedola aka DJ Cuppy, who is her sister confirmed the news also in a tweet on her official Twitter account. She wrote, “OMG OMG OMG! MY SISTER IS GETTING MARRIED @TemiOtedola.”